    "title": "Imani ndogo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "imani ndogo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Neno la Kigiriki lililotafsiriwa kama &quot;imani ndogo&quot; na maneno yanayohusiana linaonekana mara tano katika Injili ya Mathayo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:30\">Mathayo 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8\">16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">17:20</a>). Pia linaonekana mara moja katika Luka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:28\">Luka 12:28</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6-Jas1:7\">Yakobo 1:6–7</a>). Neno hili linarejelea tukio maalum, siyo kushindwa kwa kudumu.</p><p>Kwenye Mathayo, &quot;imani ndogo&quot; hutokea wakati wanafunzi wa Yesu wanapokosa maarifa au kutenda bila imani katika hali fulani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8-Matt16:11\">Mathayo 16:8–11</a>). Ikiwa mtu mara kwa mara anakosa imani, inaitwa &quot;kutoamini&quot; (tazama<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:58\"> 13:58</a>).</p><p>Baadhi ya mifano ya &quot;imani ndogo&quot; ni pamoja na:</p><ul><li><p>wakati wanafunzi hawatambui thamani yao au ulinzi wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:30\">6:30</a>);</p></li><li><p>wakati wanafunzi hawana imani katika ulinzi wa Mungu wakati wa hatari (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">14:31</a>);</p></li><li><p>wakati wanafunzi wanaposhindwa kuelewa mafundisho ya Yesu kuhusu chachu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8\">16:8</a>); na</p></li><li><p>wakati wanafunzi walishindwa kumtoa pepo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">17:20</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Hizi ni kushindwa katika hali maalum, si ukosefu kamili wa imani.</p><p>Neno <em>imani </em>linajumuisha mawazo mawili: <em>kuamini</em> (kutegemea kibinafsi kwa Bwana) na <em>imani</em> (kukubali ukweli). Shida ya Mathayo kuhusu &quot;imani ndogo&quot; inahusu mfuasi wa Yesu kukosa kuamini katika hali maalum, badala ya kushindwa kumwamini Yesu kama Bwana na Mwokozi. Yesu anataka wafuasi wake sio tu kumwamini bali pia kumtumaini, kumpenda, na kumtii (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:29\">Mathayo 7:21–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:40\">22:34–40</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:30\">Mathayo 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:29\">7:21–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:58\">13:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8\">16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">17:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:40\">22:34–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:28\">Luka 12:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6-Jas1:8\">Yakobo 1:6–8</a></p>",
